Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic scored 9 points in overtime to secure the win for the Denver Nuggets
Harrison Barnes scored 22 points and Devin Vassell 19 for San Antonio
Post-Match Reflections: Nikola Jokic had 46 points and 10 rebounds in the game
Miscellaneous Highlights: Victor Wembanyama finished with 20 points and 23 rebounds for San Antonio
Zach Collins and Russell Westbrook each received a technical foul in the first quarter
Others: The teams split the home-and-home series on consecutive nights
Julian Champagnie was 3 for 4 on 3-pointers in the two-game set against Denver
